vestment-goals-best/"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/01-Active.jpg" alt=""></a> </li><li class="series-link-item"><img decoding="async" class="series-future-post" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/02-Active.jpg" alt=""></li><li class="series-link-item"><img decoding="async" class="series-future-post" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/03-Active.jpg" alt=""></li></ul></div><div style="height:25px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><div class="vce-full-width-viz"> <a href="https://info.msci.com/l/36252/2023-08-14/xzsjy1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/msci-climate-metrics-infographic-1.jpg" alt=""></a> </div><div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-12"><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:70%"><h2 class="wp-block-heading">哪些气候指标最适合您的投资目标？</h2><p>普华永道表示，44% 的投资者认为，公司应优先考虑减少自身运营和供应链中的温室气体排放。</p><p>在我们的赞助商<a href="https://info.msci.com/l/36252/2023-08-14/xzsjy1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">MSCI</a>提供的这张图表中，我们详细分析了气候指标并提供了宝贵的见解，以帮助建立与可持续发展相一致的投资组合，而不必担心陷入绿色清洗之中。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading">投资者的基本气候指标</h2><p>以下是一些广泛使用的气候指标，按 MSCI 分类： </p><table id="tablepress-3540" class="tablepress tablepress-id-3540"><thead><tr class="row-1 odd"><th class="column-1"></th><th class="column-2">气候指标</th><th class="column-3">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody class="row-hover"><tr class="row-2 even"><td class="column-1">#1</td><td class="column-2">碳排放 EVIC 强度</td><td class="column-3">衡量每 100 万美元融资的温室气体排放量。</td></tr><tr class="row-3 odd"><td class="column-1"> #2</td><td class="column-2">潜在碳排放量</td><td class="column-3">估算公司拥有的化石燃料储备的排放量。</td></tr><tr class="row-4 even"><td class="column-1"> #3</td><td class="column-2">隐含温升 (ITR)</td><td class="column-3">评估与全球变暖情景的一致性。</td></tr><tr class="row-5 odd"><td class="column-1"> #4</td><td class="column-2">碳排放收入强度</td><td class="column-3">量化每 100 万美元收入的排放量。</td></tr><tr class="row-6 even"><td class="column-1"> #5</td><td class="column-2">化石燃料收入</td><td class="column-3">确定化石燃料相关活动的收入百分比。</td></tr><tr class="row-7 odd"><td class="column-1"> #6</td><td class="column-2">清洁技术收入</td><td class="column-3">确定来自环境和气候机会的收入百分比。</td></tr><tr class="row-8 even"><td class="column-1"> #7</td><td class="column-2">低碳转型 (LCT) 分数</td><td class="column-3">评估公司面临的气候转型机会。</td></tr><tr class="row-9 odd"><td class="column-1"> #8</td><td class="column-2">转型气候风险价值</td><td class="column-3">评估碳定价和低碳机会的成本。</td></tr><tr class="row-10 even"><td class="column-1"> #9</td><td class="column-2">自然气候风险价值</td><td class="column-3">评估因接触物理危害而增加的成本。</td></tr></tbody></table><!-- #tablepress-3540 from cache --><h2 class="wp-block-heading">选择正确的指标</h2><p><a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/sp/climate-investing-what-it-is-whats-propelling-it-and-where-to-start/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">气候投资</a>需要选择正确的衡量工具。为此，重要的是要考虑您的目的、气候战略的适用性和可接受性以及用于分析的历史数据的可用性等因素。上面的信息图包含一个流程图，旨在指导您解决几个关键问题。</p><p>例如，您想要：</p><ol><li>衡量您的投资组合对气候的影响或气候对您的投资组合的影响？</li><li>分析当前或前瞻性数据？</li><li>评估供应链的直接影响或间接影响？</li><li>评估未来潜在的排放量或预计的气温上升？</li><li>关注气候风险还是机遇？</li></ol><p> MSCI 的气候指标工具包可以帮助投资者自信地衡量、管理和报告其气候风险和机遇。 </p><div class="vc-info-box"><img decoding="async" style="max-width:28px;" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/logo.png" alt="视觉资本主义标志" class="vc-info-icon"><p class="vc-info-box-text">立即下载 MSCI<a href="https://info.msci.com/l/36252/2023-08-14/xzsjy1">气候指标工具包</a>。</p></div> <a class="vc-newsletter" href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/subscribe/"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1216" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/footer-email.gif" alt="订阅视觉资本家" /></a> <div class="wpforms-container wpforms-container-full vc-subscribe-post" id="wpforms-140438"><form id="wpforms-form-140438" class="wpforms-validate wpform